SQC WAR FNT CL CH	fhnr	dy	10
BR CH DBS BW BL		fhivx	lty	53
CH BT FLR HI4 FNT	fqrv	dty	40
HO SAB HI4 SH SQC	bcfjn	dty	33
BW INT FLR SLS STSQ	fijl	ty	30


ALL WRONG!!!

Correlate SCORE with number of post-and-bowl letters in TRAIN...
r = 0.500, p=0.022

Mean for number of post-and-bowl letters in TRAIN:
0	29.6
1	40.5
2	48.5

NICE treatise on letter effect, there, smart boy

